Introduction

ODD YOUTH is a five-member South Korean girl group under TOP MEDIA.

The group was first announced on June 27, 2024, with the opening of multiples SNS accounts, revealing their name to be "ODD YOUTH". They introduced their first member, former Girls Planet 999's contestant Myah, on September 18, 2024. The second member, Summer, was revealed on September 20, 2024. Their third member, Maika, was revealed on September 23, 2024. Kanie, the fourth member, was revealed on September 25, 2024 and, on September 27, 2024, the fifth and last member, Yeeum, was revealed.

ODD YOUTH debuted on November 1, 2024, with the release of their first single album titled "Best Friendz".
